      <title>桥水表示中国股票抛售使得估值具有吸引力</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-24/bridgewater-was-bullish-on-china-stocks-after-fund-gained-11</link>
      <description><![CDATA[桥水联合投资公司(Bridgewater Associates)在中国最近一次股市崩盘前几天向投资者表示，它对中国股市“适度看好”，因为长期的暴跌使得估值具有吸引力。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-24/bridgewater-was-bullish-on-china-stocks-after-fund-gained-11</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 24 Jan 2024 03:38:20 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>日本债券因越来越多的观点而下跌 日本央行距离加息又近了一步</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-24/japan-bonds-fall-on-growing-view-boj-a-step-closer-to-rate-hike</link>
      <description><![CDATA[日本政府债券下跌，因交易员认为日本央行周二的言论偏强硬，并提前押注未来几个月加息。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-24/japan-bonds-fall-on-growing-view-boj-a-step-closer-to-rate-hike</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 24 Jan 2024 01:13:47 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>随着冲击消退，加拿大国家铁路维持盈利增长预测</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-23/cn-railway-cnr-stands-by-earnings-growth-forecast-as-shocks-subside</link>
      <description><![CDATA[加拿大国家铁路公司 (Canadian National Railway Co.) 坚持未来几年两位数利润增长的预期，摆脱了 2023 年劳工冲突、谷物运输量低和经济低迷的影响。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-23/cn-railway-cnr-stands-by-earnings-growth-forecast-as-shocks-subside</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 23 Jan 2024 22:58:40 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>日本债券因利率押注而下跌，港股上涨：市场总结</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-23/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于加息押注加快，日本政府债券暴跌，股市下跌。亚洲其他地区股市涨跌互现，香港股市连续第二天上涨。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-23/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 23 Jan 2024 22:55:02 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>随着旅游业的复苏，泰国亿万富翁计划三年内新增 250 家酒店</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-23/thai-billionaire-plans-250-more-hotels-within-three-years-as-tourism-rebounds</link>
      <description><![CDATA[随着中国出境游客的复苏支撑全球旅游业的强劲复苏，亚洲最大的酒店集团之一美诺国际集团 (Minor International Pcl) 计划在未来三年内在其全球酒店组合中新增 250 家酒店。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-23/thai-billionaire-plans-250-more-hotels-within-three-years-as-tourism-rebounds</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 23 Jan 2024 12:06:04 GMT</pubDate>
